\section{Methodology}
This benchmark evaluates the performance of Qwen/Qwen3-Embedding-0.6B (float16) with and without Radix MLP optimization. 
The test uses MSMARCO validation query-passage pairs formatted with the Qwen3 chat template. 
Latency measurements are collected for individual embedding requests and analyzed using percentile statistics.

\section{Analysis}

The Radix MLP optimization shows an average performance improvement of 29.7\% 
compared to the baseline configuration (mean latency: 0.55s vs 0.78s).
